title: Archie Shepp - Attica Blues (1972 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DV
description:
Archie Shepp - Attica Blues (1972 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 AC3 @ 440kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.
Slight noise/crackle filtering applied (Izotope RX 2), no EQ, compression, or rear channel boost.

Converted from quad QS encoded vinyl using a SANSUI QS-D1000 VARIO MATRIX hardware decoder.


"His 1972 orchestral effort for Impulse is often a hodge-podge of jazz soul, subadolescent vocalists and political narrative, although there are moments of true power and brief but sparkling saxophone solos by the leader." ***
- Bob Blumenthal, Rolling Stone
